    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Download the Friend's Pass and play Flock of Dogs with a friend for free. If you have a friend who owns Flock of Dogs, they can bring you along on the adventure. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>(I'm currently talking to Steam about how to enable a player to own multiple Friend Slots. Right now, anyone who owns the base game can bring 1 friend along, but no more.)</i></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pilot the whale while your friend rides on a dog</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ride on a dog while your friend pilots the whale</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go on a co-op roguelike adventure</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play minigames at the Minigame Park</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can also treat this as a demo, which you can play solo or co-op, and satisfy your lifelong desire to burst through the clouds on the back of a flying dog.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Max</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
